23
00:02:00.500 --> 00:02:01.875
[Sadewo] Are you crazy?

24
00:02:01.958 --> 00:02:03.458
[Sadewo] Were you trying to drown me?

25
00:02:03.542 --> 00:02:05.125
[Bumi] No. I saw you sinking.

26
00:02:05.208 --> 00:02:06.250
That's why I helped you.

27
00:02:06.333 --> 00:02:08.167
Drowning? Your head!

28
00:02:08.250 --> 00:02:09.458
I was relaxing.

29
00:02:09.542 --> 00:02:11.542
[Sadewo] Understand
the meaning of relaxing?

30
00:02:11.625 --> 00:02:12.792
- Huh?
- Relaxing?

31
00:02:14.667 --> 00:02:16.542
I'm sorry, sir.

32
