[Rahmi] How many times have I told you?

38
00:02:38.958 --> 00:02:42.417
[Rahmi] You should go by car,
not motorbike.

39
00:02:42.500 --> 00:02:44.242
I want to look cool, Mom.

40
00:02:44.333 --> 00:02:45.393
Shh! I'm having a headache.

41
00:02:45.417 --> 00:02:46.833
Mr. Kadek's child is sick.

42
00:02:46.917 --> 00:02:48.997
Meanwhile,
there are guests to be picked up tomorrow.

43
00:02:50.208 --> 00:02:52.333
Don't be too serious.

44
00:02:52.417 --> 00:02:54.458
We'll find a solution, Mom.

45
00:02:54.542 --> 00:02:56.042
Come on. Let's go up.

46
00:02:56.125 --> 00:02:58.083
[Bumi] Oh, dear. Don't
you know how tired I am?

47
00:02:58.167 --> 00:03:00.167
[Rahmi] You can't even climb the stairs.

48
