53
00:03:31.833 --> 00:03:32.875
Hello.

54
00:03:32.958 --> 00:03:34.083
I'm Paris.

55
00:03:35.167 --> 00:03:37.292
Hello, Paris.

56
00:03:37.375 --> 00:03:38.583
But I'm not married yet.

57
00:03:38.667 --> 00:03:43.042
So, what should be written there
is "Miss Paris".

58
00:03:43.125 --> 00:03:44.625
Not "Mrs. Paris".

59
00:03:44.708 --> 00:03:46.792
Yes... Sorry, Miss.

60
00:03:46.875 --> 00:03:48.125
"Paris."

61
00:03:48.208 --> 00:03:49.375
Without "Miss".

62
00:03:49.458 --> 00:03:54.542
[upbeat music]

63
00:03:54.625 --> 00:03:55.917
I want to ride shotgun.

64
00:03:59.564 --> 00:04:00.618
[Bumi] No problem.

65
00:04:02.500 --> 00:04:03.708
Where are we going?

66
00:04:05.333 --> 00:04:06.542
Just drive first.

67
00:04:06.625 --> 00:04:13.482
[upbeat music]

68
00:04:13.577 --> 00:04:20.529
[upbeat music]

69
00:04:28.917 --> 00:04:31.292
How long will you stay in Bali?

70
00:04:31.375 --> 00:04:35.042
I've paid for the car and the driver
for one week.

71
00:04:35.125 --> 00:04:39.125
If I need them longer,
I will pay again.

72
00:04:40.292 --> 00:04:41.708
That's not what I meant.

73
00:04:43.542 --> 00:04:45.750
Are you in Bali for vacation or...

74
00:04:45.833 --> 00:04:48.667
Do I have to tell you
why I go to Bali?

75
00:04:48.750 --> 00:04:51.042
[Paris] Just ask the foreigners there.

76
00:04:51.125 --> 00:04:54.958
Why I come here
is none of your business.

77
00:04:55.042 --> 00:04:57.458
Your business is to take me to places.

78
00:04:58.292 --> 00:05:05.245
[upbeat music]

79
