[upbeat music]

80
00:05:11.704 --> 00:05:18.583
[upbeat music]

81
00:05:18.667 --> 00:05:25.667
[upbeat music]

82
00:05:25.750 --> 00:05:27.125
[Paris] Bring this for me.

83
00:05:27.208 --> 00:05:29.750
I forgot I haven't had lunch yet.

84
00:05:29.833 --> 00:05:31.167
Accompany me to eat.

85
00:05:31.250 --> 00:05:32.583
I can't eat alone.

86
00:05:33.917 --> 00:05:35.208
Sorry, but...

87
00:05:35.292 --> 00:05:38.417
No driver
has ever accompanied their guests to eat.

88
00:05:38.500 --> 00:05:40.000
[Paris] Is that so?

89
00:05:40.083 --> 00:05:43.125
Good then.
We can start that with us.

90
00:05:43.208 --> 00:05:45.708
Drivers cannot refuse
a guest's request, right?

