126
00:09:15.176 --> 00:09:16.496
[Sadewo] What are you doing here?

127
00:09:17.422 --> 00:09:19.934
Calm down, Uncle. I'm not doing anything.
I just want to enjoy the night.

128
00:09:19.958 --> 00:09:23.125
Here, come on.
I'd also like to offer you a drink.

129
00:09:23.206 --> 00:09:24.331
[Bumi] Cheers, Uncle.

130
00:09:24.417 --> 00:09:25.523
[clinking glasses]

131
00:09:27.583 --> 00:09:30.333
I didn't want to disturb you,
I was afraid you were relaxing.

132
00:09:31.708 --> 00:09:33.083
[Bumi] Hey!

133
00:09:33.167 --> 00:09:35.292
Calm down.

134
00:09:35.375 --> 00:09:36.542
You act as if you know much.

135
00:09:38.200 --> 00:09:39.575
This is my business card.

136
00:09:40.762 --> 00:09:42.202
I just finished driving for a guest.

137
00:09:44.500 --> 00:09:47.958
So, if you need anything,
just call. All good.

138
00:09:48.042 --> 00:09:52.750
[upbeat music]

139
00:09:52.833 --> 00:09:54.033
Do you come here often, Uncle?

140
00:09:54.083 --> 00:09:56.000
Hey, don't call me "Uncle".

141
00:09:56.083 --> 00:09:57.500
Just call me "Bro".

142
00:09:57.583 --> 00:09:59.625
[gigling]

143
00:09:59.708 --> 00:10:01.500
- Sir Bro.
- Bro.

144
00:10:01.583 --> 00:10:03.042
- Sir Bro...
- [Sadewo] Bro!

145
00:10:03.125 --> 00:10:05.000
- Sir Bro.
- Whatever.

146
00:10:06.542 --> 00:10:07.667
[Sadewo] Thank you.

147
00:10:07.750 --> 00:10:10.417
- [Sadewo] Do you have money to pay for this?
- All good!

148
00:10:10.500 --> 00:10:12.292
I do.

149
00:10:12.375 --> 00:10:14.417
- You're paying for my drink?
- Of course.

150
00:10:14.500 --> 00:10:16.417
- [Sadewo] Okay.
- Just enjoy it.

151
00:10:18.875 --> 00:10:20.580
- Hang on, Sir Bro. My mother.
- [Sadewo] Okay.

152
